show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/LunG74
show.description: When soft-hearted chef Aanya crosses paths with ruthless billionaire Ishaan, her world spirals into a dark game of identity, betrayal, and forbidden love. Trapped by her dying mother’s medical needs, Aanya is blackmailed by her sinister lookalike Simran into impersonating Ishaan’s estranged wife. What begins as a desperate act spirals into emotional chaos, hidden truths, and dangerous obsessions—forcing Aanya to choose between survival, justice, and the children who begin calling her "mumma."
